15:34.100 --> 15:35.810
Why don't you

15:34.100 --> 15:35.810
let me help you?

15:39.021 --> 15:41.733
I've been working late a lot.

15:41.733 --> 15:43.777
I haven't been getting

15:41.733 --> 15:43.777
much sleep.

15:43.777 --> 15:46.362
So, you're telling me this is

15:43.777 --> 15:46.362
sleep deprivation?

15:46.362 --> 15:47.947
Hmm mm.

15:49.115 --> 15:50.450
Nice try.

15:50.450 --> 15:53.369
This school is just

15:50.450 --> 15:53.369
so competitive

15:53.369 --> 15:57.081
that I need

15:53.369 --> 15:57.081
to be my best all

15:53.369 --> 15:57.081
the time.

15:57.081 --> 15:58.917
Because everyone else

15:57.081 --> 15:58.917
is so perfect.

15:58.917 --> 16:02.503
And, I just, I just

15:58.917 --> 16:02.503
don't think my work

15:58.917 --> 16:02.503
measures up.

16:05.590 --> 16:07.174
You on a scholarship?

16:07.174 --> 16:08.342
I am.

16:09.427 --> 16:11.721
And it was really

16:09.427 --> 16:11.721
hard to get.

16:13.139 --> 16:15.057
And I really don't want

16:13.139 --> 16:15.057
to lose it.

16:19.228 --> 16:21.063
CHLOE:  It's a challenge

16:19.228 --> 16:21.063
finding the right balance

16:21.063 --> 16:23.691
to stay one step ahead

16:21.063 --> 16:23.691
in moments like this.

16:26.277 --> 16:29.614
There is always some real truth

16:26.277 --> 16:29.614
under the truth you tell.

16:31.157 --> 16:34.994
But, even if I could understand

16:31.157 --> 16:34.994
what happened,

16:36.454 --> 16:38.873
even if I had the words

16:36.454 --> 16:38.873
to explain it,

16:40.333 --> 16:42.585
I couldn't trust

16:40.333 --> 16:42.585
anyone with it.

16:42.585 --> 16:44.545
( rattles doorknob )

16:44.545 --> 16:46.631
It's a mess in there.

16:49.926 --> 16:51.719
Campus security talk to you yet?

16:55.723 --> 16:58.309
I really just need to get

16:55.723 --> 16:58.309
my project back.

16:58.309 --> 16:59.769
Your project?

17:00.687 --> 17:01.855
It's ruined.

17:35.638 --> 17:37.640
She went to Bradford.

17:37.640 --> 17:38.641
In your class?

17:38.641 --> 17:40.560
The year after me.

17:40.560 --> 17:42.770
She was always kind of

17:40.560 --> 17:42.770
a loner, by choice.

17:42.770 --> 17:45.231
I mean, she didn't call too much

17:42.770 --> 17:45.231
attention to herself.

17:45.231 --> 17:47.734
I don't remember her...

17:45.231 --> 17:47.734
at all.

17:47.734 --> 17:50.236
Well, bet you won't

17:47.734 --> 17:50.236
forget her now.

17:51.863 --> 17:52.989
How's it looking?

17:55.115 --> 17:57.076
Like I'm stuck doing

17:55.115 --> 17:57.076
all the cooking.

17:57.076 --> 17:59.495
Sounds like Josh didn't get

17:57.076 --> 17:59.495
much attention today.

17:59.495 --> 18:01.873
Mark, you better give

17:59.495 --> 18:01.873
baby brother a hug.

18:03.583 --> 18:05.125
Just got off the phone.

18:05.125 --> 18:07.253
The board gave your quote

18:05.125 --> 18:07.253
a thumbs up.

18:07.253 --> 18:09.255
You can start on

18:07.253 --> 18:09.255
the benches any time.

18:11.799 --> 18:13.342
I know what you're

18:11.799 --> 18:13.342
doing, Mark.

18:14.385 --> 18:15.428
What's that?

18:16.095 --> 18:17.221
The benches.

18:18.347 --> 18:21.017
It's not going to work.

18:21.017 --> 18:23.770
You think with me spending

18:21.017 --> 18:23.770
all this time in the church

18:23.770 --> 18:27.314
that I'm going to start

18:23.770 --> 18:27.314
coming back into things.

18:27.314 --> 18:29.316
Go on.

18:29.316 --> 18:30.985
I don't want to

18:29.316 --> 18:30.985
disappoint you, brother.

18:30.985 --> 18:32.570
You can never disappoint me.

18:34.280 --> 18:37.199
I just don't like seeing you

18:34.280 --> 18:37.199
hurting like this.

18:38.451 --> 18:40.453
I don't care if you don't

18:38.451 --> 18:40.453
like it.

18:42.204 --> 18:43.414
It's not about you.

18:46.417 --> 18:47.794
Josh, you're right.

18:47.794 --> 18:49.754
I'm sorry.

18:49.754 --> 18:51.130
Dinner's ready!

18:53.507 --> 18:55.426
Lord God, we thank You

18:53.507 --> 18:55.426
for all the gifts

18:55.426 --> 18:58.096
You give us each day.

18:58.096 --> 19:01.849
We thank You even when we

18:58.096 --> 19:01.849
can't understand things,

19:01.849 --> 19:04.477
You are still in control.

19:04.477 --> 19:07.814
Give us faith to hold fast

19:04.477 --> 19:07.814
to what we know is true...

19:09.941 --> 19:12.192
CHLOE:  A lot of people tell you

19:09.941 --> 19:12.192
to let your secrets out

19:12.192 --> 19:14.194
so they don't have

19:12.192 --> 19:14.194
power over you.

19:16.322 --> 19:18.699
I don't know.

19:18.699 --> 19:21.410
Maybe I just never knew anyone

19:18.699 --> 19:21.410
I trusted that much.

19:24.080 --> 19:27.625
More often than not,

19:24.080 --> 19:27.625
when I gave myself away,

19:28.709 --> 19:30.503
it came back to hurt me.

19:32.755 --> 19:36.509
When a secret's out,

19:32.755 --> 19:36.509
then a part of you is out.

19:37.927 --> 19:40.220
It's something that belongs

19:37.927 --> 19:40.220
to others now.

19:41.848 --> 19:44.183
And you don't control

19:41.848 --> 19:44.183
the darkness anymore.

19:50.648 --> 19:52.900
( wind blowing )

20:02.368 --> 20:04.704
(whispering) You saw.

20:11.251 --> 20:13.171
You saw what happened.

20:13.171 --> 20:14.338
( screams )

20:14.338 --> 20:16.674
(whispering) You've seen it.

20:16.674 --> 20:17.675
( eerie music )

20:58.424 --> 20:59.800
( papers rustling )

21:21.822 --> 21:23.950
I think it's a premonition.

21:23.950 --> 21:25.993
Stop.

21:25.993 --> 21:27.120
I think this is saying

21:25.993 --> 21:27.120
that something bad is

21:27.120 --> 21:28.537
going to happen to you.

21:28.537 --> 21:30.497
It's just a bad dream.

21:30.497 --> 21:34.127
Yes, a dream about you!

21:34.127 --> 21:37.213
OK, I'm listening.

21:37.213 --> 21:39.548
I think that these drawings

21:37.213 --> 21:39.548
are saying

21:39.548 --> 21:42.509
that something tragic is

21:39.548 --> 21:42.509
going to happen.

21:42.509 --> 21:46.222
OK, well, then we need

21:42.509 --> 21:46.222
to talk to someone.

21:46.222 --> 21:48.141
Who?

21:48.141 --> 21:52.603
I think I know, and just

21:48.141 --> 21:52.603
hear me out.

21:52.603 --> 21:54.855
He's one of the pastors

21:52.603 --> 21:54.855
at my church.

21:54.855 --> 21:56.690
His name is Mark.

21:54.855 --> 21:56.690
He's a great guy.

21:56.690 --> 21:59.568
He's a great listener.

21:56.690 --> 21:59.568
He's... helpful.

22:00.945 --> 22:02.238
Are you serious?

22:02.238 --> 22:03.697
Like that's who you

22:02.238 --> 22:03.697
came up with?

22:03.697 --> 22:05.449
I get it, but haven't you

22:03.697 --> 22:05.449
ever wondered

22:05.449 --> 22:07.160
what it would be like

22:05.449 --> 22:07.160
to feel safe?

22:07.160 --> 22:09.829
To feel like

22:07.160 --> 22:09.829
you really matter?

22:13.207 --> 22:14.667
Just think about it.

22:14.667 --> 22:16.919
Either it helps or we're back

22:14.667 --> 22:16.919
where we started.

22:19.630 --> 22:21.507
I'll meet you there

22:19.630 --> 22:21.507
after my shift.

22:27.888 --> 22:29.932
MARK:  Living out your faith is

22:27.888 --> 22:29.932
so important.

22:30.850 --> 22:33.102
It's not easy.

22:33.102 --> 22:36.438
Never forget that when you're

22:33.102 --> 22:36.438
going through suffering...

22:36.438 --> 22:40.318
nothing can separate you

22:36.438 --> 22:40.318
from God's love.

22:42.153 --> 22:44.155
Put your hand up if you've

22:42.153 --> 22:44.155
ever been sad before.

22:45.739 --> 22:46.991
Look around.

22:49.118 --> 22:50.536
Everyone's hand is up.

22:50.536 --> 22:53.873
Everyone goes through

22:50.536 --> 22:53.873
hard times.

22:53.873 --> 22:56.959
Know that in each one

22:53.873 --> 22:56.959
of those times

22:56.959 --> 23:00.378
when you went through

22:56.959 --> 23:00.378
difficulty, God was with you.

23:00.378 --> 23:03.007
Each and every one of you.

23:03.007 --> 23:06.927
Always, especially during

23:03.007 --> 23:06.927
the most difficult times.

23:08.095 --> 23:10.388
Remember that.

23:08.095 --> 23:10.388
Know that.

23:10.388 --> 23:13.433
Take confidence in it.

23:10.388 --> 23:13.433
I sure do.

23:13.433 --> 23:15.519
( Josh sighs )

23:15.519 --> 23:17.730
( instrumental music )

23:17.730 --> 23:21.525
♪ It's hard to understand

23:17.730 --> 23:21.525
this life we're living ♪

23:23.319 --> 23:28.115
♪ More down than up, more lost

23:23.319 --> 23:28.115
than found these days ♪

23:31.077 --> 23:35.122
♪ And everybody's searching

23:31.077 --> 23:35.122
for the reasons ♪

23:36.623 --> 23:41.212
♪ of a pain and shame,

23:36.623 --> 23:41.212
it just won't go away ♪

23:43.923 --> 23:46.717
CHLOE:  Have you ever wondered

23:43.923 --> 23:46.717
if God was really out there?

23:49.553 --> 23:53.015
Like I said, things usually

23:49.553 --> 23:53.015
ended very bad for me

23:53.015 --> 23:55.351
when I put my faith

23:53.015 --> 23:55.351
in someone else.

23:57.144 --> 24:00.231
And that's what led me

23:57.144 --> 24:00.231
to my wall.

24:00.231 --> 24:04.484
I'd been hiding my secrets

24:00.231 --> 24:04.484
here for so long,

24:04.484 --> 24:07.113
but my situation never seemed

24:04.484 --> 24:07.113
to get any better.

24:08.488 --> 24:10.783
Maybe Rebecca was right.

24:10.783 --> 24:13.119
Maybe it was time to try

24:10.783 --> 24:13.119
something else.

24:13.119 --> 24:15.788
♪ Be with us now ♪

24:15.788 --> 24:18.791
♪ If love can conquer

24:15.788 --> 24:18.791
every fear, ♪

24:18.791 --> 24:21.585
♪ please wash away

24:18.791 --> 24:21.585
these tears ♪

24:21.585 --> 24:25.923
♪ Be with us now ♪

24:36.934 --> 24:38.018
Hey.

24:39.812 --> 24:40.813
Hey.

24:41.605 --> 24:42.648
How you doing?

24:45.359 --> 24:46.402
Good.

24:49.155 --> 24:50.239
Everything okay?

24:51.657 --> 24:55.286
Yeah, I'm just waiting

24:51.657 --> 24:55.286
for somebody.

24:56.745 --> 24:58.205
Well, I'm glad you're

24:56.745 --> 24:58.205
feeling better.

25:07.047 --> 25:08.799
Josh?

25:07.047 --> 25:08.799
Yeah.

25:11.677 --> 25:13.511
Do you know Rebecca?

25:14.430 --> 25:16.056
Rebecca?

25:16.056 --> 25:18.017
I don't think so.

25:18.017 --> 25:19.643
We're meeting

25:18.017 --> 25:19.643
with Pastor Mark.

25:20.686 --> 25:22.771
What, tonight?

25:22.771 --> 25:24.940
Well, there's no one left in

25:22.771 --> 25:24.940
the church...

25:24.940 --> 25:26.608
Pastor Mark's not here?

25:26.608 --> 25:27.651
No.

25:31.947 --> 25:33.699
Hey, do you have

25:31.947 --> 25:33.699
a phone?

25:33.699 --> 25:34.700
Maybe you can call her?

25:34.700 --> 25:36.076
N-no, that's fine.

25:36.076 --> 25:37.911
I think I know where

25:36.076 --> 25:37.911
she might be.

25:37.911 --> 25:38.996
But...

25:41.165 --> 25:42.458
( street noises )

25:44.584 --> 25:46.170
( door closes )

26:12.405 --> 26:13.697
Help you, honey?

26:13.697 --> 26:15.282
Yeah uh...is Rebecca here?

26:15.282 --> 26:16.992
Um, I'm not sure.

26:16.992 --> 26:18.576
There's a table of kids

26:16.992 --> 26:18.576
around the corner.

26:18.576 --> 26:21.288
Maybe she's back there.

26:31.090 --> 26:33.633
Uh...did she have

26:31.090 --> 26:33.633
to work late?

26:33.633 --> 26:36.387
Who's that?

26:33.633 --> 26:36.387
Rebecca.

26:36.387 --> 26:38.931
I'm sorry, sweetie,

26:36.387 --> 26:38.931
I don't know who

26:36.387 --> 26:38.931
you're talking about.

26:38.931 --> 26:40.140
Is she not back there

26:38.931 --> 26:40.140
with those kids?

26:40.140 --> 26:42.518
No. She's a waitress here.

26:42.518 --> 26:44.144
Are you sure you have

26:42.518 --> 26:44.144
the right place?

26:44.144 --> 26:46.522
Yes, Rebecca.

26:46.522 --> 26:47.981
Everything OK?

26:47.981 --> 26:50.109
She's looking for someone

26:47.981 --> 26:50.109
named, Rebecca

26:50.109 --> 26:52.319
that she says works here.

26:52.319 --> 26:54.071
Ain't nobody named

26:52.319 --> 26:54.071
Rebecca work here.

26:54.071 --> 26:56.614
OK, did she set

26:54.071 --> 26:56.614
you guys up for this?

26:56.614 --> 26:57.741
Will you tell her

26:56.614 --> 26:57.741
that I went to

26:56.614 --> 26:57.741
the church?

26:57.741 --> 26:59.243
OK? I waited there

26:57.741 --> 26:59.243
for her.

26:59.243 --> 27:00.953
Honey, there is nobody

26:59.243 --> 27:00.953
here named Rebecca.

27:14.133 --> 27:15.342
Will you stop saying that!

27:15.342 --> 27:16.469
Of course, there's

27:15.342 --> 27:16.469
a Rebecca here.

27:16.469 --> 27:18.095
She works here!

27:18.095 --> 27:19.679
I don't know what you want me

27:18.095 --> 27:19.679
to tell you, sweetie.

27:19.679 --> 27:21.390
There's no one here.

27:19.679 --> 27:21.390
Stop calling me "sweetie"!

27:21.390 --> 27:22.600
OK, either you get out

27:21.390 --> 27:22.600
of here or I'm calling

27:21.390 --> 27:22.600
the cops.

27:22.600 --> 27:23.976
You know what?

27:22.600 --> 27:23.976
Go ahead.

27:23.976 --> 27:25.352
Uh look, maybe we better

27:23.976 --> 27:25.352
go outside.

27:25.352 --> 27:26.728
They won't tell me

27:25.352 --> 27:26.728
where Rebecca is.

27:26.728 --> 27:28.063
OK, then I'll help you

27:26.728 --> 27:28.063
find Rebecca.

27:28.063 --> 27:29.565
Lola, do not call

27:28.063 --> 27:29.565
the cops.

27:29.565 --> 27:30.899
Josh, you know her?

27:29.565 --> 27:30.899
JOSH: Yes.

27:30.899 --> 27:32.109
You need to get her

27:30.899 --> 27:32.109
out of here.

27:32.109 --> 27:33.402
You need to relax.

27:33.402 --> 27:34.778
Chloe, Rebecca's not here

27:34.778 --> 27:36.780
and they're going

27:34.778 --> 27:36.780
to call the cops.

27:36.780 --> 27:38.449
and I'll help

27:36.780 --> 27:38.449
you find her but

27:36.780 --> 27:38.449
we need to get out of here.

27:45.705 --> 27:47.749
Chloe!

27:47.749 --> 27:49.418
We don't need any crazy

27:47.749 --> 27:49.418
people in here.

27:49.418 --> 27:51.462
You call the cops.

27:53.506 --> 27:54.756
Hey!

27:54.756 --> 27:56.800
Hey, slow down.

27:54.756 --> 27:56.800
Get away from me!

27:56.800 --> 27:58.469
I'm just trying

27:56.800 --> 27:58.469
to help you.

27:58.469 --> 27:59.761
I don't need your help, OK?

27:58.469 --> 27:59.761
I need to find Rebecca

27:59.761 --> 28:00.887
and something's

27:59.761 --> 28:00.887
happened to her

28:00.887 --> 28:02.473
and they all know it.

28:02.473 --> 28:03.599
I told her that something

28:02.473 --> 28:03.599
was going to happen.

28:03.599 --> 28:05.142
Why don't we try this?

28:05.142 --> 28:06.310
Tell me where she lives

28:05.142 --> 28:06.310
and we'll go to my truck

28:06.310 --> 28:07.603
and I will take you there.

28:09.896 --> 28:13.233
She, um...

28:09.896 --> 28:13.233
Why can't I remember?

28:13.233 --> 28:15.152
OK, look, you're confused,

28:13.233 --> 28:15.152
it's okay to be confused.

28:15.152 --> 28:17.321
I'm not confused, OK?

28:15.152 --> 28:17.321
So stop treating me like a baby!

28:17.321 --> 28:18.447
I'm not treating you

28:17.321 --> 28:18.447
like a baby!

28:18.447 --> 28:19.697
Just tell me.

28:19.697 --> 28:21.241
Does she live in town

28:21.241 --> 28:22.535
because wherever you want

28:21.241 --> 28:22.535
to go, I'll take you.

28:22.535 --> 28:23.577
( siren blasts )

28:25.078 --> 28:26.288
CHLOE: Oh no.

28:30.250 --> 28:33.337
Miss? Hold it right there.

28:33.337 --> 28:35.130
OFFICER: We got a call

28:33.337 --> 28:35.130
that you were a little upset.

28:50.187 --> 28:51.689
( papers rustling )

28:57.736 --> 28:58.862
This is her?

29:02.824 --> 29:06.745
Yeah, I talked to the owner

29:02.824 --> 29:06.745
of the diner.

29:06.745 --> 29:10.499
He said nobody named Rebecca

29:06.745 --> 29:10.499
worked there right now.

29:10.499 --> 29:12.501
She was at the hospital

29:10.499 --> 29:12.501
the other night

29:12.501 --> 29:14.545
when you came in.

29:14.545 --> 29:16.714
She was?

29:16.714 --> 29:18.507
She was in the room when

29:16.714 --> 29:18.507
you came to talk to me.

29:18.507 --> 29:22.886
Chloe, no one was in that

29:18.507 --> 29:22.886
hospital room with you.

29:27.641 --> 29:28.934
( sighs )

29:32.229 --> 29:34.231
How long have you

29:32.229 --> 29:34.231
been seeing these?

29:36.442 --> 29:38.527
I've been seeing them

29:36.442 --> 29:38.527
in pieces for a while now.

29:40.028 --> 29:41.739
What, are you going to put me

29:40.028 --> 29:41.739
under mental health arrest?

29:41.739 --> 29:44.283
That's not up to me.

29:44.283 --> 29:49.455
I'm just here trying

29:44.283 --> 29:49.455
to sort through all this

29:44.283 --> 29:49.455
right now.

29:49.455 --> 29:52.791
I'm going to show you

29:49.455 --> 29:52.791
a picture and I want you

29:49.455 --> 29:52.791
to tell me

29:52.791 --> 29:56.587
if it looks

29:52.791 --> 29:56.587
like your friend,

29:52.791 --> 29:56.587
Rebecca Cole.

30:01.300 --> 30:02.342
That her?

30:03.135 --> 30:04.720
Yes.

30:04.720 --> 30:06.263
Where is she?

30:04.720 --> 30:06.263
Just calm down.

30:06.263 --> 30:07.765
No. What happened to her?

30:07.765 --> 30:10.934
Where did she go?

30:07.765 --> 30:10.934
Just one thing at a time.

30:10.934 --> 30:13.437
How did you meet Rebecca,

30:10.934 --> 30:13.437
do you remember?

30:14.688 --> 30:16.356
At the diner.

30:16.356 --> 30:17.775
My mom and I used to go

30:16.356 --> 30:17.775
and she would wait on us.

30:17.775 --> 30:19.568
The girl in that picture?

30:17.775 --> 30:19.568
Yes.

30:19.568 --> 30:21.528
You're positive.

30:19.568 --> 30:21.528
Yes.

30:21.528 --> 30:23.196
And you became friends?

30:21.528 --> 30:23.196
Where is she?

30:23.196 --> 30:24.323
Chloe, you're right.

30:26.325 --> 30:29.202
Rebecca worked at

30:26.325 --> 30:29.202
the Parkside Diner.

30:32.080 --> 30:34.333
But she went missing

30:32.080 --> 30:34.333
12 years ago.

30:49.222 --> 30:50.265
That can't be true.

30:52.142 --> 30:54.770
You were a little girl.

30:56.396 --> 30:57.648
Maybe you don't remember.

30:59.650 --> 31:02.486
