And sometimes it only lets

51:21.245 --> 51:24.582
you know about them

51:24.582 --> 51:27.543
when you're ready.

51:27.543 --> 51:31.672
The curtain drops and memories

51:27.543 --> 51:31.672
can come flooding back.

51:33.758 --> 51:36.761
It was that thought that

51:33.758 --> 51:36.761
led me back here.

51:36.761 --> 51:38.512
( thunder rumbles )

51:40.890 --> 51:42.892
This place and I are

51:40.890 --> 51:42.892
forever connected now.

51:42.892 --> 51:45.978
MAN: Come on, Rebecca,

51:42.892 --> 51:45.978
let me give you a ride.

