53:27.121 --> 53:28.580
Hey, Josh.

53:28.580 --> 53:30.248
Hi, Lola.

53:32.417 --> 53:34.670
I hear the cops

53:32.417 --> 53:34.670
are looking

53:32.417 --> 53:34.670
for your friend.

