Yeah.

53:38.549 --> 53:41.217
You know,

53:38.549 --> 53:41.217
I had no idea

53:41.217 --> 53:43.846
that Rebecca she was talking

53:41.217 --> 53:43.846
about the other night

53:43.846 --> 53:45.097
was Rebecca Cole.

