Yeah.

53:48.934 --> 53:50.394
You knew her, huh?

53:50.394 --> 53:51.937
Sure.

53:51.937 --> 53:54.314
Some of us around here

53:51.937 --> 53:54.314
are lifers, you know.

53:57.776 --> 53:59.319
Thanks, Lola.

53:57.776 --> 53:59.319
Yeah.

54:02.322 --> 54:03.991
Hey, you find

54:02.322 --> 54:03.991
your girl yet?

54:04.950 --> 54:07.161
Nope.

