Police told us to keep

54:07.161 --> 54:09.205
a look out for her,

54:09.205 --> 54:12.416
but she hadn't

54:09.205 --> 54:12.416
been around.

54:12.416 --> 54:14.459
Hey, what's wrong

54:12.416 --> 54:14.459
with her?

54:17.379 --> 54:18.630
I'm not sure.

54:20.049 --> 54:21.217
Hey, thanks.

54:29.141 --> 54:30.475
Thought that

54:29.141 --> 54:30.475
