55:27.699 --> 55:29.868
She was healing,

55:27.699 --> 55:29.868
not hurting.

55:29.868 --> 55:31.411
She was having

55:29.868 --> 55:31.411
the best year

55:29.868 --> 55:31.411
of her life.

55:31.411 --> 55:33.538
Sometimes you don't see

55:31.411 --> 55:33.538
the whole picture, Josh.

