You can be

55:35.082 --> 55:36.708
on top of the world

55:35.082 --> 55:36.708
the one minute

55:36.708 --> 55:38.752
and the bottom

55:36.708 --> 55:38.752
can fall out in

55:36.708 --> 55:38.752
the next.

