You of all people

55:39.962 --> 55:41.588
should know that.

55:43.381 --> 55:45.050
Don't make this

55:43.381 --> 55:45.050
about Hannah.

55:45.050 --> 55:47.427
Josh, I'm sorry.

55:47.427 --> 55:50.097
But I can't help but wonder

55:47.427 --> 55:50.097
if it is about her.

