Here's the truth.

55:53.558 --> 55:55.560
The police

55:53.558 --> 55:55.560
gave up on Rebecca.

55:55.560 --> 55:57.771
They saw her as

55:55.560 --> 55:57.771
a troubled kid

55:55.560 --> 55:57.771
and they filed her away.

