Josh, please.

56:00.565 --> 56:02.318
Sit and talk a bit.

56:02.318 --> 56:03.944
What's the point?

56:08.573 --> 56:09.908
( sighs )

56:35.893 --> 56:38.979
CHLOE:  Sometimes when you

56:35.893 --> 56:38.979
decide not to give up

56:35.893 --> 56:38.979
on something,

56:40.605 --> 56:42.482
it drives you to pursue it

