( metal clanging )

56:50.074 --> 56:52.159
It makes you risk everything.

56:52.993 --> 56:55.537
( metal clanging )

56:59.624 --> 57:02.253
You look for answers.

57:06.257 --> 57:09.176
You look for hope.

57:15.682 --> 57:17.559
There's probably a million

57:15.682 --> 57:17.559
lost explorers

57:17.559 --> 57:20.104
for every one who

57:17.559 --> 57:20.104
finds an answer.

57:21.813 --> 57:23.274
( water sloshes )

57:26.110 --> 57:28.862
Then something comes along

57:26.110 --> 57:28.862
that you didn't expect.

57:30.739 --> 57:32.574
And suddenly...

57:32.574 --> 57:34.034
( dramatic instrumental music )

57:34.034 --> 57:35.869
( thud )

57:38.580 --> 57:40.332
You realize you're

57:38.580 --> 57:40.332
on the right path.

