Hey.

59:52.339 --> 59:54.132
What's up?

59:54.132 --> 59:56.051
I gotta ask you something.

59:56.051 --> 59:58.303
Are you OK?

59:56.051 --> 59:58.303
Yeah, I'm fine.

59:58.303 --> 59:59.930
Look, I was with

59:58.303 --> 59:59.930
Rebecca's foster mom

59:59.930 --> 01:00:02.266
and she gave me

59:59.930 --> 01:00:02.266
this old photo

59:59.930 --> 01:00:02.266
of you two.

01:00:03.934 --> 01:00:05.143
I remember this.

01:00:06.353 --> 01:00:07.729
Look at Rebecca.

01:00:07.729 --> 01:00:09.314
You see that old truck

01:00:07.729 --> 01:00:09.314
in the background?

01:00:09.314 --> 01:00:11.233
You don't know whose truck

01:00:09.314 --> 01:00:11.233
that is by chance, do you?

01:00:11.233 --> 01:00:12.568
A customer, maybe?

01:00:12.568 --> 01:00:14.570
Looks like Matt Barnes'

01:00:12.568 --> 01:00:14.570
old truck.

01:00:14.570 --> 01:00:16.280
I'm not sure, why you asking?

01:00:16.280 --> 01:00:17.822
Who's Matt?

01:00:16.280 --> 01:00:17.822
He's the night cook.

01:00:17.822 --> 01:00:19.324
He was there yesterday

01:00:17.822 --> 01:00:19.324
when you were in.

01:00:19.324 --> 01:00:20.534
I'm pretty sure he had

01:00:19.324 --> 01:00:20.534
a truck like that

01:00:20.534 --> 01:00:21.910
before he bought his bike.

01:00:21.910 --> 01:00:23.203
Is he at

01:00:21.910 --> 01:00:23.203
the restaurant?

01:00:23.203 --> 01:00:24.288
No, he's got

01:00:23.203 --> 01:00:24.288
the weekends off.

01:00:24.288 --> 01:00:25.414
He's sleeping.

01:00:26.623 --> 01:00:28.041
Does he live in town?

01:00:28.041 --> 01:00:29.626
Out on Trimmer Road.

01:00:29.626 --> 01:00:31.086
Where on Trimmer?

01:00:31.086 --> 01:00:32.546
Gray house past

01:00:31.086 --> 01:00:32.546
the tracks.

