01:00:35.591 --> 01:00:36.508
It's a long story.

01:00:36.508 --> 01:00:38.343
Thanks, Lola.

01:00:38.343 --> 01:00:39.928
Josh...

01:01:03.285 --> 01:01:04.620
JOSH: You OK?

