They say God can heal

01:01:08.373 --> 01:01:10.792
your broken heart.

01:01:12.836 --> 01:01:14.421
But I've never felt Him.

01:01:15.713 --> 01:01:18.550
He's always seemed

01:01:15.713 --> 01:01:18.550
so far away.

01:01:23.930 --> 01:01:26.057
I think someone hurt you

01:01:23.930 --> 01:01:26.057
very much.

01:01:27.725 --> 01:01:28.768
Is that true?

01:01:31.813 --> 01:01:33.148
You can trust me.

01:01:34.566 --> 01:01:35.609
I know.

01:01:39.779 --> 01:01:40.614
You can trust me, Chloe.

01:01:40.614 --> 01:01:41.657
I know!

01:01:51.500 --> 01:01:53.210
I never knew my father.

01:01:55.629 --> 01:02:00.217
As long as I can remember,

01:01:55.629 --> 01:02:00.217
it was just my mom and me.

01:02:01.885 --> 01:02:03.720
She dated a few guys.

01:02:05.263 --> 01:02:06.806
Some of them were very nice.

01:02:10.352 --> 01:02:12.103
Some of them

01:02:10.352 --> 01:02:12.103
weren't so nice.

01:02:14.565 --> 01:02:17.067
( sniffs )

01:02:17.067 --> 01:02:21.321
I-I didn't like being around

01:02:17.067 --> 01:02:21.321
when they were home.

01:02:21.321 --> 01:02:23.323
Especially when my mom

01:02:21.321 --> 01:02:23.323
wasn't there.

01:02:26.076 --> 01:02:30.747
So I would go and hang

01:02:26.076 --> 01:02:30.747
down by the river.

01:02:31.873 --> 01:02:33.875
Under the bridge.

01:02:39.005 --> 01:02:40.840
Does your mom know?

01:02:40.840 --> 01:02:41.966
( scoffs )

01:02:44.595 --> 01:02:45.679
That is not on you.

01:02:45.679 --> 01:02:47.264
How do you know?

01:02:47.264 --> 01:02:49.349
It's not on you.

01:02:49.349 --> 01:02:51.309
( tearfully ) How do you know?

01:02:53.144 --> 01:02:54.396
You did nothing wrong.

01:02:56.189 --> 01:02:59.317
It's not on you.

01:02:56.189 --> 01:02:59.317
It's not on you.

01:02:59.317 --> 01:03:00.860
