01:04:03.340 --> 01:04:05.091
But when you've run

01:04:03.340 --> 01:04:05.091
out of options...

01:04:07.969 --> 01:04:10.221
your choices become

01:04:07.969 --> 01:04:10.221
more desperate.

01:04:14.100 --> 01:04:16.060
Are you sure you're OK

01:04:14.100 --> 01:04:16.060
with this?

01:04:42.379 --> 01:04:44.673
If you want to hang back,

01:04:42.379 --> 01:04:44.673
it's OK.

