Well, I think it's time

01:07:07.732 --> 01:07:09.567
you told the police.

01:07:11.319 --> 01:07:12.654
Think you're ready for that?

01:07:14.447 --> 01:07:15.824
Yeah.

01:07:23.206 --> 01:07:24.708
( typing )

01:07:25.750 --> 01:07:27.335
Sarge.

01:07:25.750 --> 01:07:27.335
Yeah.

